  LOG(creator_total_consumptions + 1) × 0.10

-- Cap at +10 points to prevent dominance
CREATOR_BOOST = LEAST(CREATOR_REPUTATION, 10)
Why:

Proven creators likely produce quality
But new creators can still rank if recipe is good
Boost is small (max 10 points vs 100 point scale)


